strings.Value: "I thought super-clever professors like you don't even take a shit without a crowd of armed guards. Forget about an expedition to the Stolen Lands!"

"Yes, I have to admit, coming here may not have been my finest idea. Although the notes I've taken during our travels are quite valuable. It would be a pity if they were never to see the light, because their author ended his journey in a troll's stomach."
